opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 7th day of March, 2016, the Application for Leave to File Original Process is GRANTED, and the Petition for Writ of Mandamus and/or Extraordinary Relief is DENIED.
Justice EAKIN did not participate in the consideration or decision of this matter.
